{"type":"message","id":"ddf0d62c","parentId":"a11dd3d2","timestamp":"2026-02-18T18:05:13.365Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-02-18 20:05 GMT+2] OPERATION: LIVE LOGGER & TOKEN INJECTION.\n\n1.  **Terminal Observer (`scripts/live_logger.py`):**\n    *   Create script:\n        *   Tail `logs/bot.log`.\n        *   If line contains \"ERROR/CRITICAL\": Append to `logs/live_alerts.log`.\n        *   If line contains \"Trade\": Send Alert to Telegram (simulated).\n\n2.  **Token Fix (Hardcode for Session):**\n    *   Edit `scripts/broadcast_log.py`.\n    *   *Inject:* `os.environ[\"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\"] = \"8461845004:AAE3eAnAyohsRh9XMrkv3pNx56iACKmOuws\"` (This is safe as it's local only).\n\n3.  **Rust Check (Main Process Fallback):**\n    *   Since `cargo` failed in main exec, try `docker run --rm rust cargo --version`.\n    *   If Docker fails -> Accept \"NO RUST\" and enable Python Legacy Mode permanently in `ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json`.\n\n4.  **Autonomy Verdict:**\n    *   Assess: Can I restart myself? Can I see errors?\n    *   Blocker: Lack of System Admin rights prevents Rust installation.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Logger status.\n    *   Token fix confirmation.\n    *   Autonomy Level (Percentage)."}],"timestamp":1771437913363}}
